==Slovak==
=== Personal Pronoun ===
'''[[sa#Slovak|sa]]''' ''or'' '''seba'''
# [[oneself]]
===Usage note===
* Replaces the [[accusative]] of any personal pronoun whenever the [[object]], whether expressed or implied, is of the same [[person]] as the [[subject]].
*'''vidím sa v zrkadle'''&mdash;''I see myself in the mirror
*'''Koho vidíš v zrkadle? Seba.'''&mdash;''Whom do you see in the mirror? Myself.''
[[Category:Slovak pronouns]]

